---
// Pure CSS animated background - no JS needed
---

<div class="fixed inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
  <div class="absolute top-0 -left-4 w-96 h-96 bg-brass-700 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-20 animate-blob"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-0 -right-4 w-96 h-96 bg-cognac-800 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-20 animate-blob animation-delay-2000"></div>
  <div class="absolute -bottom-8 left-20 w-96 h-96 bg-burgundy-900 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-20 animate-blob animation-delay-4000"></div>
</div>
